<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
  <div class="bg-white shadow-xl rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-50 to-white px-8 py-6 border-b border-gray-100">
      <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
        <i class="fas fa-hands-helping text-4xl text-red-600"></i>
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800">Fraternal Assistance</h1>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="p-8 pb-12">
      <div class="prose text-gray-700 mb-8 space-y-4">
        <p>Fraternal Assistance is a Spiritist practice of individual spiritual support and guidance, grounded in empathy, active listening, and sincere care. It aims to help individuals understand and face their challenges through self-knowledge and the values of the Spiritist teachings.</p>
        <p>This support is offered respectfully, without judgment or imposition, encouraging moral strengthening and inner transformation through the living practice of the Gospel.</p>

      <div class="bg-red-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-red-400 mb-8">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-red-800 mb-3 flex items-center">
          <i class="fas fa-heart mr-2"></i>
          What Makes It Special
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-red-500 mr-2 mt-1"></i>
            <span>Private and respectful sessions held at our centre</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-red-500 mr-2 mt-1"></i>
            <span>Carried out by trained and prepared volunteers</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-red-500 mr-2 mt-1"></i>
            <span>No religious imposition or pressure</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4 flex items-center">
          <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt text-red-500 mr-2"></i>
          How to Receive Assistance
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 bg-red-100 h-10 w-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
              <span class="text-red-600 font-bold">1</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-800 mb-1">Schedule a Session</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">You may request a booking through our website or in person at our centre</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 bg-red-100 h-10 w-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
              <span class="text-red-600 font-bold">2</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-800 mb-1">Confirmation Call</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Our team will contact you to confirm the appointment, according to availability</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 bg-red-100 h-10 w-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
              <span class="text-red-600 font-bold">3</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-800 mb-1">Private Meeting</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Each session lasts approximately 30 minutes and is held confidentially in a safe and welcoming environment. Duration may vary slightly depending on the nature of the case.</p>
              <p>Sessions are preferably booked in advance but may also be offered during the centreâ€™s opening hours, depending on the availability of trained volunteers.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 text-center">
          <%= link_to "Contact Us to Schedule", contact_path, class: "inline-flex items-center px-5 py-3 bg-red-100 hover:bg-red-200 text-red-700 rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors" %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-10">
        <%= link_to services_path, class: "inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-200 rounded-lg text-gray-700 font-medium transition-colors" do %>
          <i class="fas fa-arrow-left mr-2"></i>
          Back to Services
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
